column1: #Text=To raise funding and awareness for children living with AIDS in Africa , the tallest mountain peak in every state in the United States will be scaled this spring .
#Text=The American Foundation for Children with AIDS ( AFCA ) , in partnership with the American Alpine Institute , is sponsoring " Climb Up the 50 .
